high_descs: Turn around and go to the counter.
Pick up the ladle on the right side of the counter.
Carry the ladle a few steps to the left and face the sink.
Place the ladle in the sink and turn the water on. Turn the water off and pick up the ladle again.
Take the ladle and move to the right a step.
Open the top right drawer and place the ladle inside.
anns.task_desc: Rinse a ladle and put it away in the drawer.

high_descs: Move to the counter to the right of the sink
Pick up a scoop from the counter
Move to the sink to the left of you
Clean the scoop in the sink and pick it back up
Move to the counter to the right of the sink
Place the scoop in the drawer farthest from the sink
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned scoop in the drawer farthest to the right of the sink.

high_descs: Turn and move to stand at the counter to the right of the kitchen sink.
Pick up the spoon from the counter.
Carry the spoon to the kitchen sink.
Place the spoon in the sink, turn on the water, wash the spoon, and then remove it from the sink.
Carry the spoon to return to the counter to the right of the kitchen sink.
Open the drawer on the right beneath that counter space and place the spoon inside.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed spoon in a drawer.
